survey_response.review_text:
I am Ekambaram, 68 years old, was requiring a Full Mouth Rehabilitation, as I was suffering with many dental issues for years. I gone into right hands, Dr Nandakumar and Dr Sumedha Nandakumar of Sai Faciomaxillary & Dental Centre, where my treatment was scheduled for about two months, with 15-16 sittings. Today, I returned to my 40s, with a complete cure of all my ailments. 

I appreciate the excellent professional service rendered by Dr Sumedha, Dr Sivaranjani and their team and I adore their focussed attention in treating me. The clinic is well maintained and conforming to NABH standards, which demands customised care and total satisfaction of the patients.

The ambiance of the clinic is so cozy, and highly hygienic with premier interiors. The Clinic is fully equipped with latest and updated equipments, with the state-of-art technology, where the patients will get an international treatment at Indian cost.

At the Reception, Ms Fathima is so courteous to the patients, ensures they are regularly followed up, fix the appointments and makes them meeting the doctors, without any long waiting. I saw her, as a multi-tasking girl with good administration skills.

I could find Dr. Sumedha, never compromises, on the quality of her treatment, as well the accessories she uses, for her patients. Dr Sivaranjani, is a good support to the doctors and a good learner. Overall, I had and an awesome experience, through their personal care and painless treatment. 

Infact, they don’t look for the Patients’ satisfaction, but for a ‘Patients’ Delight’, where untold requirements of the patients are also addressed and given right solutions. 

Sai Faciomaxillary & Dental Centre, is the best destination for the dental issues of any sort, on a most competitive cost as on date, in Chennai, as of now. 

They make you SMILE, Confidently.
Got my second root canal and zirconium crown done. I feel relaxed even during the treatment knowing well I am in good hands.

If you have any problems in your teeth etc, don't wait and don't be worry about treatment, go to Dental temple Sai Dental,
You realise 💯safe and safety for us like me 60 plus.
Good Doctors with team on mutispecility.

I had been to Sai dental clinic for a chipped tooth filling. Despite her busy schedule, Dr. Sumedha was kind enough to give me an appointment when I expressed my concern which was duly addressed. My experience was truly amazing. The staff exhibited expertise, friendliness and concern.Thank you so much for everything.
Dr was very kind and explained process stage by stage which was very much helpful to overcome the fear.
Excellent  patient care good doctor friend lines  good facilities. Overall satisfaction . Good medical care

Polite  kind and friendly. 
Good treatment. 
Nominal expenses. 
Poor people will also like the doctor

My Doctor  Sumedha Nandakumar, She is very friendly and well experieced  . Ten years back I came here for RCT in my right side tooth. Its not giving me any problem till date. . **** **** ****   *** **** ** **** ********* *** ** ********

Known Dr Sumedha,& her husband Dr Nandakumar over two decades.At various stages they were our family dental care givers.My daughters had their dental treatments done here.My eldest  daughter always has her dental check up when ever she visits India  with Dr. Sumedha,
Dr Sumedha is an expert & very well experienced in her field,with lot of experience. Her communication level is excellent & clarifies all doubts one may have about the treatment.
Very friendly. Both Dr. Sumedha and Dr. Nandakumar assured my oral lichen wasn't alarming. Scaling was done to perfection.
